{"tid":328401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[三權合作]法官：你要投訴打人 稍移玉步投訴警察課 呢度講法律唔係講政治！","createTime":"2017-07-19T14:15:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T16:37:56.000Z","uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"44aabac21dbe7990a2d3c899316405f5121a64f4","tid":328401,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:15:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170719/56975280\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170719%2F56975280&d=dG8WLkYDNMcC3X2tWQInyARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=a9278f92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170719%2F56975280&h=8274f503\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170719/56975280</a><br />\n<br />\n【刑事藐視法庭】法官：唔好將我嘅法庭變咗做show嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n佔旺清場的刑事藐視法庭案，當日有份清場的總督察林志源繼續作供。辯方於盤問時向林指，不是想作出任何指控，但從當日片中可見有警員打人。控方反對有關提問，辯方解釋指林的說法將會關乎其證供可信性，辯方或會傳召片段中該名被打的被捕男子任辯方證人。<br />\n<br />\n法官陳慶偉聞言即批評辯方說法，質疑警員有否打人與本案有何關係，直言<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「唔好將我嘅法庭變咗做show嘅地方，你要投訴佢打人，就稍移玉步去投訴警察課。呢度講法律，唔係講政治！」</span></strong> 聆訊下午繼續。<br />\n<br />\n根本司法機關都已經淪陷，三權合作人治社會已經開始"},{"pid":"376355be5e4fbc18dab275d2fdf0c4b30bb8fd16","tid":328401,"uid":521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:16:22.000Z","msg":"做show<br />\n<br />\n有哂立場"},{"pid":"743e086c77025887531c877b06a92399378cb932","tid":328401,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:19:32.000Z","msg":"殖民地法庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae32f79b8f4b6171d34afc46a0ae90c840687b2","tid":328401,"uid":60665,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:21:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做show<br />\n<br />\n有哂立場</blockquote><br />\n前幾年都係低級裁判官先有d咁既官<br />\n而家連高等法院都淪陷埋<br />\n加埋dq案既判決<br />\n司法獨立可以話係差唔多玩完"},{"pid":"40078f159fedd10ca454567474c9bc3e0b